description stealing a car.

307
00:20:21.687 --> 00:20:25.781
- Where?
- Defiance. Ohio.

308
00:20:27.157 --> 00:20:28.751
Someone's going down today.

309
00:20:36.575 --> 00:20:39.341
I know. mami. I know.

310
00:20:50.045 --> 00:20:55.411
- Sara... I paid your bail.
- You took your time.

311
00:20:55.787 --> 00:20:57.723
I'm the governor.
I do have things that...

312
00:20:57.755 --> 00:20:59.641
Go to hell. Dad.

313
00:20:59.735 --> 00:21:00.663
You keep this up.

314
00:21:00.805 --> 00:21:03.351
this may be the only place
I'll be able to see you.

315
00:21:03.485 --> 00:21:05.690
Do you even want to
hear my side of things?

316
00:21:05.786 --> 00:21:08.132
Not particularly. Sara. no.

317
00:21:08.278 --> 00:21:12.472
Especially when I have no
idea whose "side" you're on.

318
00:21:12.617 --> 00:21:14.353
But I do know this.

319
00:21:14.445 --> 00:21:17.790
Somebody is going to go down because
