on the ground. okay?

400
00:27:44.426 --> 00:27:46.723
So. how're you feeling. huh?

401
00:27:47.146 --> 00:27:49.160
You keeping your appetite up?

402
00:27:49.305 --> 00:27:52.122
Sorta. I guess.

403
00:27:52.357 --> 00:27:55.370
That's good. That's real good.

404
00:27:56.118 --> 00:28:00.021
Oh. God. it's so good to see you.
baby girl.

405
00:28:02.328 --> 00:28:05.062
Do you understand what Daddy
