406
00:28:05.095 --> 00:28:06.121
Sorta.

407
00:28:06.267 --> 00:28:09.602
But the kids at school
have been sayin' stuff.

408
00:28:09.798 --> 00:28:11.902
Okay. what have
they been saying?

409
00:28:12.048 --> 00:28:15.391
They're saying you're on TV
because you're a bad man.

410
00:28:17.756 --> 00:28:19.770
And what do you think?

411
00:28:20.376 --> 00:28:23.152
I think if I were someplace

412
00:28:23.246 --> 00:28:25.692
and they wouldn't let
me leave to see you.

413
00:28:25.787 --> 00:28:28.422
I wouldn't do what
they said. either.

414
00:28:30.786 --> 00:28:33.552
Well. you know what?

415
00:28:33.697 --> 00:28:37.983
We are gonna be together real soon.
I promise you.

416
00:28:38.087 --> 00:28:39.830
But Daddy needs you
to do him a favor.

417
00:28:39.867 --> 00:28:42.122
I need you to get a
message to Mommy. okay?

418
00:28:42.258 --> 00:28:43.332
Okay.

419
00:28:44.216 --> 00:28:48.970
Now I need you to tell her if
she understood what I told her

420
00:28:49.165 --> 00:28:52.743
and if she is willing
to trust Daddy...

421
00:28:53.397 --> 00:28:59.991
