porch light at 7:00. okay?

422
00:29:00.136 --> 00:29:01.770
Can you remember that?

423
00:29:01.878 --> 00:29:03.562
That's a good girl.

424
00:29:03.655 --> 00:29:06.481
Dede. stay away from
the gate. honey.

425
00:29:08.888 --> 00:29:12.183
Daddy gotta get going.
okay sweet pea?

426
00:29:14.197 --> 00:29:18.011
- I love you. Daddy.
- I love you. too. baby.

427
00:29:27.065 --> 00:29:28.281
There.

428
00:29:36.615 --> 00:29:38.350
It's not much further now.

429
00:29:48.485 --> 00:29:52.212
Okay. they moved off the Interstate.
heading North on Route 38.

430
00:29:52.305 --> 00:29:53.380
Talk to me.

431
00:29:55.096 --> 00:29:56.573
Where?

432
00:29:57.087 --> 00:29:59.121
There's a patrolman who thinks
he's has Fernando Sucre

433
00:29:59.155 --> 00:30:01.191
pulled over outside of
Latrobe. Pennsylvania.

434
00:30:01.227 --> 00:30:02.591
Get in touch with
the local dispatch.

435
00:30:02.627 --> 00:30:06.010
Make it clear that we want this
man in custody. not in a body bag.

436
00:30:06.108 --> 00:30:10.390
Dead men can't tell us where their
friends are. Yeah. you got it.

437
00:30:52.906 --> 00:30:54.801
It's gotta be.
it looks just like him.

438
00:30:55.988 --> 00:30:58.192
Yeah. I'll take care of it.

439
00:30:59.166 --> 00:31:00.221
I will.

440
00:31:09.067 --> 00:31:10.521
Mr. Miller...

441
00:31:11.126 --> 00:31:15.220
I'm gonna have to ask you to place
your arms outside the vehicle please.

442
00:31:17.356 --> 00:31:19.371
Mr. Miller.
I need to see some hands.

443
00:31:54.745 --> 00:31:56.951
- You ready?
- Yeah.

444
00:31:59.317 --> 00:32:00.091
Now.

445
00:32:14.657 --> 00:32:16.011
This is the one.

446
00:32:24.115 --> 00:32:25.091
Do you see him?

447
00:32:25.237 --> 00:32:27.303
Nope. Maybe he didn't
get your message.

448
00:32:37.625 --> 00:32:41.962
They've stopped.
Couple miles up ahead. There's...

449
00:32:42.055 --> 00:32:43.752
There's nothing up
there. What...?

450
00:32:44.137 --> 00:32:45.821
What are they waiting on?

451
00:32:46.247 --> 00:32:48.451
Or who?

452
00:32:53.636 --> 00:32:56.083
All right. that's good.
that's good. that's good.

453
00:33:17.455 --> 00:33:19.091
Oh. come on.

454
00:33:19.417 --> 00:33:20.590
Come on!

455
00:33:23.315 --> 00:33:24.581
Go red.

456
00:33:24.867 --> 00:33:26.500
Now. go red!

457
00:33:53.288 --> 00:33:54.833
Just one more thing.

458
00:33:56.687 --> 00:33:57.992
Do you trust me?

459
00:34:00.586 --> 00:34:01.711
Of course.

460
00:34:02.548 --> 00:34:05.222
How do you throw the
hunter off the scent?

461
00:34:05.555 --> 00:34:07.290
Get rid of the prey.

462
00:34:07.845 --> 00:34:08.733
Remember.

463
00:34:09.285 --> 00:34:13.103
once I hit scan. we'll have about
30 seconds before it reaches 103.7.

464
00:34:13.248 --> 00:34:14.322
And then she blows?

465
00:34:14.506 --> 00:34:17.510
- That's right. Ready?
- Yeah.

466
00:34:36.545 --> 00:34:37.852
All right. let's go.

467
00:34:42.665 --> 00:34:44.972
Wait. wait. wait.
wait. wait. wait.

468
00:34:48.856 --> 00:34:50.172
Something's wrong.

469
00:34:51.187 --> 00:34:52.360
What happened?

470
00:34:52.915 --> 00:34:56.113
I don't know.
