474
00:35:13.598 --> 00:35:15.742
We're going to have to
set it off manually.

475
00:35:15.757 --> 00:35:17.323
The car could blow
any second. Michael.

476
00:35:17.357 --> 00:35:20.130
Well. the feds are going to
be here in about two minutes.

477
00:35:20.168 --> 00:35:22.893
If it doesn't look like we're dead.
we will be.

478
00:35:23.085 --> 00:35:24.531
Rock. paper. scissors?

479
00:35:24.995 --> 00:35:27.302
- Linc?
- It's my turn.

480
00:35:43.408 --> 00:35:45.470
Better pray for reception.

481
00:35:53.945 --> 00:35:58.281
How many stations
between 102.1 and 103.7?

482
00:35:58.327 --> 00:36:02.571
Way out here?
Just one. probably.

483
00:36:26.388 --> 00:36:27.271
Oh!

484
00:36:39.947 --> 00:36:41.211
Where's Maricruz?

485
00:36:41.398 --> 00:36:44.363
- Hey. Hey. look. man...
- No. no. no. Petey. You look.

486
00:36:44.458 --> 00:36:46.522
I haven't slept in 72 hours.

487
00:36:46.718 --> 00:36:48.461
I've seen a man's
hand get chopped off.

488
00:36:48.495 --> 00:36:50.890
I've been...
I've been shot at. dug up a grave.

489
00:36:50.988 --> 00:36:53.712
stolen a car.
jumped on a fricking a train.

490
00:36:54.035 --> 00:36:56.152
so please.
just tell me where she is.

491
00:36:56.247 --> 00:36:57.982
Hey. Fernando. slow down. man.

492
00:36:58.078 --> 00:37:00.772
I was trying to tell you.
but you hung up the phone. man.

493
00:37:00.806 --> 00:37:03.013
The wedding- it's in Vegas.

494
00:37:04.407 --> 00:37:05.670
The city?

495
00:37:05.857 --> 00:37:08.351
Yeah. and they left
a few hours ago.

496
00:37:18.586 --> 00:37:20.430
Wait. no. no. no.
No. no. no. no. no.

497
00:37:20.516 --> 00:37:22.911
Come on. hey.
come on. Fernando!

498
00:37:23.008 --> 00:37:24.243
It's pristine. man.
It's just...

499
00:37:24.277 --> 00:37:26.521
Gonna be back to you in one piece.
I promise.

500
00:37:26.528 --> 00:37:28.670
Can we go back to the
part where I said no?

501
00:37:28.686 --> 00:37:32.362
- I wish I had another choice.
- You do have a choice. Come on. man.

502
00:37:32.458 --> 00:37:36.931
It's a 1952 Ural motorbike. bro.
If you so much as scratch it...

503
00:37:36.985 --> 00:37:39.333
No scratches... I promise.

504
00:37:42.015 --> 00:37:47.011
She's the love of my life. bro.
I got to do something.

505
00:37:47.208 --> 00:37:50.313
- You look like hell.
- I've been through hell. papi.

506
00:37:50.495 --> 00:37:53.702
Now I just got to get to Vegas.

507
00:38:01.285 --> 00:38:05.201
Um. hi. I'm Sara. and I. uh...

508
00:38:08.346 --> 00:38:09.283
Um...

509
00:38:13.077 --> 00:38:15.190
over the years.
I've worked with...

510
00:38:15.796 --> 00:38:20.182
more than a few people who had a
history of addiction. and. uh...

511
00:38:21.335 --> 00:38:25.913
I would tell 'em that I could understand
what they were going through because I...

512
00:38:26.238 --> 00:38:27.972
used to be just like them.

513
00:38:28.118 --> 00:38:30.560
I used to be an addict. too.

514
00:38:31.026 --> 00:38:33.512
And I think. uh...

515
00:38:34.208 --> 00:38:39.302
I think that what's becoming
clear to me is that...

516
00:38:39.575 --> 00:38:41.443
the reason I
understood them is...

517
00:38:41.535 --> 00:38:43.461
because I am like them.

518
00:38:43.697 --> 00:38:45.333
Um...

519
00:38:46.126 --> 00:38:49.082
I never used to be an addict.
I. uh...

520
00:38:52.427 --> 00:38:54.863
Hi. my name is Sara.
and I'm an addict.

521
00:38:54.955 --> 00:38:56.651
Hi. Sara.

522
00:39:01.505 --> 00:39:03.813
Hi. my name's Lance.
and I'm an addict.

523
00:39:03.906 --> 00:39:05.103
Hi. Lance.

524
00:39:07.006 --> 00:39:10.582
I guess a lot of what Sara
just said resonates with me

525
00:39:10.725 --> 00:39:12.501
in what I'm going through.

526
00:39:14.687 --> 00:39:16.993
Put in all that work.
break out of prison.

527
00:39:17.085 --> 00:39:19.762
only to end up dead at
the bottom of a ditch.

528
00:39:19.908 --> 00:39:21.502
Kind of sad really.

529
00:39:22.008 --> 00:39:23.562
So. which one of them was it?

530
00:39:27.497 --> 00:39:30.640
- Shales.
- Shales?

531
00:39:30.747 --> 00:39:33.183
Scofield. Might be Scofield.

532
00:39:33.416 --> 00:39:36.293
You're probably going to find
his brother in there. too.

533
00:39:37.405 --> 00:39:40.463
Oscar Shales is this guy
Mahone tracked for a while.

534
00:39:40.607 --> 00:39:43.283
Nasty little bottom feeder.
You know the type.

535
00:39:43.745 --> 00:39:47.371
