539
00:40:19.478 --> 00:40:22.072
They're going to get the lab
results back from the accident. man.

540
00:40:22.106 --> 00:40:26.440
- We'll be in Mexico by that time.
- Provided the transport comes through.

541
00:40:36.025 --> 00:40:38.093
Oh. come on. baby.

542
00:40:49.756 --> 00:40:52.581
In the Rainbow Room.

543
00:40:53.236 --> 00:40:57.713
Do you remember that beautiful
spot where we took that picture.

544
00:40:57.807 --> 00:41:00.533
the one by the window?

545
00:41:01.046 --> 00:41:07.502
I am going to be waiting in
that spot one week from now.

546
00:41:40.136 --> 00:41:45.422
