the doctor?

554
00:42:20.907 --> 00:42:22.173
Sara?

555
00:42:24.025 --> 00:42:26.852
I. uh... I don't know.

556
00:42:28.055 --> 00:42:30.920
We should get moving.
Next town is a few miles away.

557
00:42:31.388 --> 00:42:34.351
Yeah. that's fine.
I can catch a bus from there.

558
00:42:35.325 --> 00:42:37.063
Thanks again. Nika.

559
